data.description: Stunning single level home located in Woodland!  3 bed 2.5 bath, open concept home!  Home features light and bright living area with an updated kitchen w/granite counter tops, custom cabinets, stainless steel appliances and over sized pantry.  The living room has a gas burning fire place connected to a large dining room.   Newer flooring, interior and exterior paint and automatic shades.  Primary with walk in closet and ensuite bath with walk in shower & soaking tub. Oversized laundry off of the garage.  So many quality upgrades!  Exterior features private beautifully landscaped yard with covered patio, newer roof, large fenced backyard, storage shed and a 3-car garage.  Paved drive on 2 acres!  Located 2 miles from I5!
